gal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.017402, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn95060049, 1910-06-30, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ak", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["tanana", "united states", "tanana (alaska)", "alaska", "newspapers"], "subject_headings": ["Tanana (Alaska)--Newspapers", "Alaska--Tanana", "United States--Alaska--Tanana"], "subjects": [{"alaska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alaska&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"tanana": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:tanana&fo=json"}, {"tanana (alaska)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:tanana+%28alaska%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-23T00:42:07.575Z", "title": "Tanana leader (Tanana, Alaska), June 30, 1910", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95060049/1910-06-30/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95060049/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn95060049", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/ef8fc707-df1b-5b39-bc66-c83a68f1be5f"], "batch": ["ak_kodiakriverotter_ver02"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1909", "description": ["Weekly Began in Feb. 1909? -v. 2, no. 25 (Aug. 25, 1910). Description based on: Vol. 1, no. 19 (July 1, 1909). Yukon Valley news (Tanana, Alaska : 1910) 2993-6160 (DLC)sn 95060050 (OCoLC)33136970"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-02", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-02"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95060049/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [65.1705807, -152.081943], "location": ["tanana", "alaska", "united states"], "location_str"